/news/story/6811/5278482</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>美國在2月25日啟動了2年期、5年期、7年期的公債拍賣。這幾種天期的公債會受聯準會2023－24年的貨幣政策影響。拍賣結果十分慘淡，7年期公債的投標倍數（衡量需求的指標）創新低，導致市場更加擔心債券需求低迷。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5109900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cw.com.tw%2Farticle%2F5109900&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=a281a1ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5109900</a>"},{"pid":"4126e6b59b511ae9e3df7b7a4d2487ea09a59ea7","tid":2436144,"uid":352740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c91b971cb7d4d17e5084dbcc8dc192c0057803","tid":2436144,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053564a76d756c8177e0e27a9520b0fbed1d1712","tid":2436144,"uid":352740,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f688edb7cc723696c195f8c7379f20588af35ab","tid":2436144,"uid":153102,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"其實冇關係,報紙佬求其搵野up下配合個市<br />\n戇鳩先會信"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"依樣真跟本係藉口<br />\n18-19年債息成2-3厘咪又係升<br />\n往往都係過後揾跌市升市原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家聽左合理就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如一啲股票冇盈利都可以炒到好高PE<br />\n大家都係聽佢嘅未來願景夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"你係咪講緊TxxA..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"Tesla唔覺有咩問題<br />\n只不過佢炒過龍<br />\n回調返400-300會入少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得佢係科技軟件股多過汽車股"},{"pid":"3041c4e77b988430c0bc8387f0ddc251e7b123e8","tid":2436144,"uid":20805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98277f752acaa71ab672925c8bab295ce8291103","tid":2436144,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"我岩岩睇書，話債券的價格會比股票跌先。<br />\n咁債劵加息即係平左？<br />\n咁但之前美國債劵加息，但雜誌話d科技股跌。但點解其餘又跌得咁